  "body": "Since chainId is defined as `u64`, but the cheat code `vm.chainId` is uint256 which will cause overflow.\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/014f7c4445dc815e07ae1b469ca31d266bd59fd8/config/src/chain.rs#L15\r\n- https://github.com/foundry-rs/forge-std/blob/be5c649c897519cdae29c5a0ad00d4c1351e4dcc/src/Vm.sol#L20\r\n\r\nReproduce in fuzzing testing\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\nfunction testFuzzChainId(uint256 chainId_) external {\r\n    vm. chainId(chainId_);\r\n}\r\n```",
