    "body": "I started working on this issue, but its fuzzing test does not fail in my environment. \r\nAlso, a similar fuzzing test exists at https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/testdata/cheats/Travel.t.sol and does not fail.\r\nCould you publish the full source code for the failing fuzzing test?\r\n\r\nIt seems that `Id(u64)` of `Chain` is used in `foundry.toml` and has no relation to `cheats.chainId`. \r\n`cheats.chainId` seems to change `chain_id`(`U256`) of `CfgEnv`, not `id(u64)` of `Chain`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/bluealloy/revm/blob/5572e303c7963727538883de817f9b52ca304f50/crates/revm/src/models.rs#L221\r\n```rs\r\npub struct CfgEnv {\r\n    pub chain_id: U256,\r\n    pub spec_id: SpecId,\r\n```\r\n",
